A wheel rests on the ground and supports a vertical load of [`[$load]`] [`kN`] at its central axle, as shown in the diagram. The three equally-spaced spokes are identical. They are [`[$l]`] [`m`] long, [`[$d]`] [`mm`] in diameter, and made of steel with [`E = 210`] [`Gpa`], [`\nu = 0.3`] and density [`\rho=[$rho]`] [`kg/m^3`]. You may assume that the rim is rigid compared with the spokes, and does not significantly deform. Determine the force in each of the three spokes. 

[`F_{AB}=`] [____]{"$fab"} [`kN`]  
[`F_{AC}=`] [____]{"$fac"} [`kN`]  
